text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: 27 days until the election. Vote early if you can. Let’s end this nightmare! It’s vital.
title: October 7, 2020: VOTE it’s VITAL.
